Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:52.39,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也输入邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:58.26,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又将其删除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.66,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这样的每一天
